Ld=kd(I/r2)max(0,n⋅l)
L_d = k_d(I/r^2)max(0,n\cdot l)
L​d​​=k​d​​(I/r​2​​)max(0,n⋅l)
Ls=ks(I/r2)max(0,n⋅h)p
L_s = k_s(I/r^2)max(0,n\cdot h)^p
L​s​​=k​s​​(I/r​2​​)max(0,n⋅h)​p​​
La=kaIa
L_a = k_aI_a
L​a​​=k​a​​I​a​​
